(Part 13 of 13) “Good News for Muslims” explores Islam, the Quran, Christianity, the Bible, and Jesus Christ. Shahbaz, who grew up in Iran, is Steve Wohlberg’s guest in this fascinating, eye-opening 13-part series that will inspire your heart and bring peace to your soul. https://www.goodnewsformuslims.com
